Craig Gordon is poised to become the first new signing of Ronny Deila’s Celtic reign.

The former Scotland goalkeeper has been attracting interest from Rangers, Hearts and Motherwell.

But Sportsmail understands the 31-year-old underwent a medical for Celtic at a private hospital in Glasgow on Tuesday.

